The monotone sources contain some files developed by third parties,
that may qualify as "independent and separate works in themselves"
for the purpose of GPLv2 section 2, if separated from monotone itself.
Upstream provides a comprehensive statement of authorship and licensing
for these files; please see /usr/share/doc/monotone/AUTHORS.gz.

The directory /usr/share/doc/monotone/contrib contains files which are
included in the upstream source distribution, and may be useful in
conjunction with monotone proper, but are not considered part of
monotone.  Upstream does not provide definitive copyright and
licensing information for all these files, but asserts that "to the
